  "lastUpdatedOn": "2012-09-03",
  "religion": "Kerr is a Nichiren Buddhist.",
  "politicalViews": "Kerr is all about environmentalism, but hasn't seemed to weigh in on any other mainstream political issues.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Miranda Kerr was born Sydney, Australia and grew up in Gunnedah, New South Wales, Australia."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Kerr's Australian upbringing and her English, Scottish, and French family heritage",
      "sourceTitle": "Miranda Kerr's Biggest Runway Mishap? Flying Shoe!",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.justjared.com/2009/09/11/miranda-kerrs-biggest-runway-mishap-flying-shoe/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " imply an undoubtedly Christian tradition. However, Kerr went off her European religious rails and took up Nichiren Buddhism.",
      "sourceTitle": "Hey, Did You Know Miranda Kerr Is Buddhist?",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.patheos.com/blogs/faithgoespop/2011/11/hey-did-you-know-miranda-kerr-is-buddhist-and-an-aries/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " Coincidentally, Kerr's famous husband, Orlando Bloom, is also a Nichiren Buddhist, both of whom"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": ", and both"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " are members of the Japanese branch of Buddhism called Soka Gakkai International.",
      "sourceTitle": "Miranda Kerr",
      "sourceUrl": "http://ethnicelebs.com/miranda-kerr"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " It's unclear if one influenced the other or it was a commonality that helped to move along their courtship."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Kerr actively practices her religion, chanting for 20 minutes twice daily, practicing yoga and meditation, and reading widely on topics of spirituality. She said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5,
      "parentId": 4
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I believe that everyone is looking for the answers, but the answers are within ourselves. Buddhism feels right for me… I believe we're all equal and we all have our purpose in life. We all have our karma that we need to fulfill and I'm here fulfilling mine.",
      "sourceTitle": "Miranda's model life",
      "sourceUrl": "http://web.archive.org/web/20071211001041/http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0,22049,22730119-5006011,00.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I predict many frat boys converting to Nichiren Buddhism in the very near future.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 7
    },
    {
      "parentId": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Green politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 8
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Kerr wants to make a difference in the world. Wisely listening to her father, Kerr realized that this may be difficult if she sticks only to modeling. She said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 10,
      "parentId": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I've always had a burning desire to help people and make a difference in the world. I didn't know how I could do that in modelling when it can be such a fake world. But my dad told me I could make a difference by being true to myself and teaching people what I've learned about spirituality, health and nutrition.",
      "sourceTitle": "Miranda's model life",
      "sourceUrl": "http://web.archive.org/web/20071211001041/http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0,22049,22730119-5006011,00.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "…And environmentalism. Kerr has played up her strengths for the cause of a greener world, appearing nude and chained to a tree on the cover of Rolling Stone to promote the cause of saving the trees for Australia's koala bears.",
      "sourceTitle": "7 Hot Female Models Who Are Also Environmentalists",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.treehugger.com/culture/7-hot-female-models-who-are-also-environmentalists.html"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " Furthermore, she was the global ambassador for the Earth Hour program,",
      "sourceTitle": "Earth Hour Ambassador Miranda Kerr",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.thedailygreen.com/going-green/tips/earth-hour-47032002"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " an organization set up to shine light (pun intended) on environmental issues by asking everyone in the world to turn off their lights for one hour per year."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I predict many frat boys spending an hour drinking in the dark in the very near future."
    }
  ],
